---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Amrich Pharma" description="How Amrich Pharma protects farmer data under India's DPDP Act 2023 and GDPR. Transparent, secure, and farmer-first data practices.">
  <section class="hero-band-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy: How We Protect Your Data</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--on-dark-soft); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Last Updated: November 1, 2024 — DPDP Act 2023 &amp; GDPR Compliant
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Farmer-First Data Promise</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        At Amrich Pharma, your trust is our most valuable asset. We collect only the data needed to serve you better — nothing more, nothing less. Every piece of information you share helps us deliver customized pond protocols, disease interventions, and seasonal support tailored to your farm. We never sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding surface-soft">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>What Data We Collect &amp; Why</h2>
      <div style="overflow-x: auto; margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background: var(--surface-strong);">
              <th style="padding: var(--space-sm); text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);">Data Type</th>
              <th style="padding: var(--space-sm); text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);">Why We Collect It</th>
              <th style="padding: var(--space-sm); text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);">Legal Basis</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Name, Phone, WhatsApp</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Customized dosage plans</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Consent + Legitimate Interest</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Farm Location</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Regional specialist assignment</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Consent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Pond Size, Species, Challenges</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Accurate protocols</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Consent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Website Usage (Cookies)</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Site improvement</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Consent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Testimonials / Yield Data</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Share farmer results</td>
              <td style="padding: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);">Explicit Consent</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-lg); font-weight: 600;">
        We never sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>How We Protect Your Data</h2>
      <ul style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); padding-left: var(--space-lg); display: grid; gap: var(--space-sm);">
        <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> TLS 1.3 in transit + AES-256 at rest</li>
        <li><strong>Access Control:</strong> Role-based access, limited to essential personnel</li>
        <li><strong>Retention:</strong> Data retained for 24 months, then securely deleted</li>
        <li><strong>DPDP Compliance:</strong> Full alignment with India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act 2023</li>
        <li><strong>GDPR Alignment:</strong> Principles of data minimization, purpose limitation, and transparency</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding surface-soft">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Cookies &amp; Analytics</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        We use Google Analytics 4 with anonymized IP addresses. Only essential cookies are set — no advertising or tracking cookies. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Under DPDP Act 2023 and GDPR, you have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); padding-left: var(--space-lg); display: grid; gap: var(--space-xs);">
        <li><strong>Access</strong> — Request a copy of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Correction</strong> — Update inaccurate information</li>
        <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Objection</strong> — Withdraw consent for processing</li>
        <li><strong>Portability</strong> — Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@amrichpharma.com">privacy@amrichpharma.com</a> to exercise any of these rights.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding surface-soft">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Data Protection Officer</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Amrich Pharma<br />
        Plot No. 2, Sainath Nagar, Shivaji Mandpeshwar Road, Dahisar, Mumbai-400068<br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@amrichpharma.com">privacy@amrichpharma.com</a><br />
        Phone: 97123 35338
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        We respond to all data requests within 72 hours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        This policy was last updated on November 1, 2024. We will notify registered users of material changes via email or WhatsApp. Continued use after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding hero-band-dark" style="text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color: var(--on-dark);">Questions About Your Data?</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--on-dark-soft); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Email Our Data Protection Officer
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:privacy@amrichpharma.com" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg); display: inline-flex;">
        privacy@amrichpharma.com
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
